data.description: Welcome to your dream oasis! Nestled on 1.4 acres of picturesque land, you’ll be captivated by the perfect blend of privacy & tranquility.  Inside the home, you'll discover a haven of modern living. Home offes beautiful spacious kitchen with soft close cabinets. Stone gas fireplace in living that is open to the kitchen. Primary bedroom downstairs - You’ll love the master bath with large walk in shower. Boasting 3 very spacious secondary bedrooms upstairs. Outside you will find a 30x50 metal workshop with an additional 17x12 workshop accessible from the back. Was being used workshop area as well as an entertainment area with the incredible bar on the inside. Also has covered deck in back with a hot tub waiting for you! This residence offers ample space for both relaxation and entertainment. Tankless Hot Water Heater (2017), Roof (2020), A/C upstairs (2021)   Don’t miss out on this Rare Gem!
